---
const MOTO_IMG = "https://d36hbw14aib5lz.cloudfront.net/310519663568009244/9oWeQAjFk7GoTWpFXegazj/moto_estrada-WBtucu3AC4pLKfQ4csSnLc.webp?Expires=1807954676&Signature=JM7f4S39Gwos6ycaWvUIOphRn2gE-Eh1pT0j6Y4r11vQZZ3394a2~l~B2ZcX1PVUK-mitiyA539MYCJKGzBcVsZ654NBy5Z8g-HozxDg3DYE3m1KDVh4ZHSYTHDtKj8t9gch9SVXMZnBnCTPdTBxpwLKD-m3oo69MAu4qGF-3gRYPPgUrfJNjNtxxH~W-W1vdnveED98o-Esve9tOKYq6-DckPdyRxTZNqe4s~hQFnXVhxLISdZZqmiV0bTTUri3asqNLBVIODk6TEjgBvTKu9tZFsB82FtejIJr1T9n45DnW~yBcjZT4szDD6G9xyviwdDGNESQxpcnwaOR0mcxMA__&Key-Pair-Id=K1MP89RTKNH4J";

const SKILLS = [
  { label: "Fotografia Aérea", pct: 95 },
  { label: "FPV Drone", pct: 85 },
  { label: "Fotografia Terrestre", pct: 90 },
  { label: "Edição & Pós-prod.", pct: 88 },
];
---

<section id="sobre" class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center">
    <!-- Image side -->
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[3/4] max-w-sm mx-auto md:mx-0">
        <img src={MOTO_IMG} alt="Flávio Sena na estrada" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 right-4 bottom-4 border pointer-events-none" style="border-color: oklch(0.72 0.18 65 / 0.3);"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Floating coordinate card -->
      <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 md:right-0 border p-4 max-w-[180px]" style="background: oklch(0.12 0.006 285); border-color: oklch(0.72 0.18 65 / 0.3);">
        <p class="coord-text mb-1" style="color: oklch(0.72 0.18 65);">Localização</p>
        <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">São Paulo, Brasil</p>
        <p class="coord-text text-white/40 mt-1">23°32'S · 46°38'W</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text side -->
    <div>
      <p class="coord-text mb-4" style="color: oklch(0.72 0.18 65 / 0.8);">/ 02 — Sobre</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        Sena, <span class="italic" style="color: oklch(0.72 0.18 65);">o outro</span> olhar
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-white/70 leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 300;">
        <p>Sou Flávio Sena, fotógrafo e piloto de drone apaixonado por descobrir o Brasil de perspectivas que poucos têm a chance de ver. Minha câmera e meu drone são extensões do meu olhar — sempre buscando o ângulo que conta a história completa.</p>
        <p>As viagens de moto são meu portal para lugares remotos, cachoeiras escondidas e estradas que o Google Maps ainda não mapeou direito. Cada quilômetro percorrido é uma oportunidade de capturar a beleza bruta do Brasil.</p>
        <p>Trabalho com drones DJI Air 2S e plataformas FPV para criar imagens aéreas que vão desde o cinematográfico suave até o dinâmico e acrobático. O pôr do sol é meu horário favorito.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Skills -->
      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {SKILLS.map((skill) => (
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between mb-1.5">
              <span class="text-xs text-white/60" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;">{skill.label}</span>
              <span class="coord-text" style="color: oklch(0.72 0.18 65 / 0.8);">{skill.pct}%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-px bg-white/10 relative">
              <div
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-px transition-all duration-1000"
                style={`width: ${skill.pct}%; background: oklch(0.72 0.18 65);`}
              ></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Social links -->
      <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/sena_o_outro/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm transition-colors"
          style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;"
          onmouseover="this.style.color='oklch(0.72 0.18 65)'"
          onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.6)'"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
          Instagram
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.tiktok.com/@senaooutro"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm transition-colors"
          style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;"
          onmouseover="this.style.color='oklch(0.72 0.18 65)'"
          onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.6)'"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19.59 6.69a4.83 4.83 0 01-3.77-4.25V2h-3.45v13.67a2.89 2.89 0 01-2.88 2.5 2.89 2.89 0 01-2.89-2.89 2.89 2.89 0 012.89-2.89c.28 0 .54.04.79.1V9.01a6.33 6.33 0 00-.79-.05 6.34 6.34 0 00-6.34 6.34 6.34 6.34 0 006.34 6.34 6.34 6.34 0 006.33-6.34V8.69a8.18 8.18 0 004.78 1.52V6.76a4.85 4.85 0 01-1.01-.07z"/></svg>
          TikTok
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
